ctrl + รถ                        toggle terminal
ctrl + '                        toggle comment
(ctrl + k) + (ctrl + num)       fold all (decide scope by number)
(ctrl + k) + (ctrl + j)         unfold all

ctrl + d                        highlight text (press again to select next occurrance)
ctrl + l                        highlight line
alt + up/down arrow             move line
alt + shift + up/down arrow     move & copy line

alt + click                     multiple cursor

